Applications: Practical examples of how RFVPs enhance neural network optimization, biological rhythm stabilization, and quantum state coherence.
Broader Implications: A discussion of how RFVPs contribute to systemic resilience, interconnectivity, and evolutionary progress within the fractal continuum.
